snippet.title: Coffeehouse Crime
snippet.description:
Welcome to Coffeehouse Crime. My name's Adrian, and I like to report on solved, unsolved and strange true crime cases. Pull up a seat and grab a coffee to my weekly videos! 

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/coffeehousecrime
For case suggestions and personal enquiries: coffeehousecrime@gmail.com
For business enquiries: coffeehousecrime@delkatalents.com
